      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute beauty in person! It's in truly pristine, mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've taken incredible care of it, and it's looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. This is a rare find that's ready for your next big road trip. Come take a look!",
