    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the legendary S54-powered platform, maintained to a fastidious standard. The 3.2L high-revving inline-six features a perfectly calibrated double VANOS system and individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power through a crisp Getrag six-speed manual gearbox. The chassis integrity is absolute, featuring a documented rear subframe reinforcement and a factory-spec suspension overhaul with fresh bushings and dampers to ensure zero deflection under load. This specimen retains its original paint depth across all panels and an immaculate undercarriage free of oxidation. Equipped with the M-Variable differential lock and riding on pristine forged alloy wheels, this vehicle offers the precise turn-in and mechanical feedback that defined the golden era of naturally aspirated performance. A concours-level find for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
